Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.69,0:00:07.46,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,As I recall, back when we were in school, Kanie acted something like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.15,0:00:10.32,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,Hey Kanie, you've got supplementary lessons today!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.27,0:00:17.78,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,Oh, shoot. Sorry, I've got plans today, so I'm leaving early.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.19,0:00:22.64,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,Back then, I could never in a thousand years have imagined that Kanie of all people
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.64,0:00:26.14,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,would become a teacher, or that things would turn out like {\i1}this{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.29,0:00:32.30,Signs,,0,0,0,,The 25 Year Old High School Girl
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.29,0:00:32.30,Signs,,0,0,0,,{\an1}Episode 2: In the Nurse's Office Bed
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.30,0:00:35.30,Signs,,0,0,0,,Nurse's Office
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.73,0:00:37.28,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,Just for you...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.81,0:00:42.18,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,I'll give you a special lesson I can't give to children.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.60,0:00:43.70,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.65,0:00:47.56,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,Not that!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.77,0:00:50.52,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,No more!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.52,0:00:55.06,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,You're already so wet, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.19,0:00:58.49,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,You actually want it, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.49,0:01:01.04,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,Y-You're wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.47,0:01:08.02,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,No! Don't, Kanie. Any more and I'll...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.69,0:01:14.46,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,They'll hear you outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.35,0:01:18.34,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,That's a good girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.59,0:01:39.56,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,Wow, it's really sloshing around.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.93,0:01:44.25,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,Stop it already!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.69,0:01:48.65,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,What's that? Are you OK with being found out, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.65,0:01:54.72,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's right, if my secret is exposed it won't be just me that gets in trouble, but also Kaho.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.26,0:01:57.56,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But doing something like this...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.73,0:01:59.87,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,Natori.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.87,0:02:00.30,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.79,0:02:12.48,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,In the end, Kanie didn't go any further.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.52,0:02:12.48,Signs,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fad(500,0)}Nurse's Office
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.17,0:02:17.00,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,I suppose I can keep your secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.03,0:02:22.44,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,Your personality is the polar opposite of Kaho Miyoshi.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.15,0:02:26.79,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,If you keep acting all timid like that, you'll be found out in no time.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.89,0:02:31.52,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,Are you really going to keep my secret, Kanie?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.42,0:02:38.86,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,And if you don't want to be assaulted by punks like Aida, you'd better try and stay close to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.23,0:02:42.80,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It was {\i0}you{\i1} who assaulted me just now...{\i0}{Reminder: Rape is not OK}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.41,0:02:45.28,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,I'm a teacher here, you understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.07,0:02:49.92,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,So while we're at school, address me properly if you don't want to be found out.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.91,0:02:51.98,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,Y-Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.01,0:03:00.78,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This whole thing is off to a terrible start.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.51,0:03:10.28,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,Let's see... Boys in Class B...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.04,0:03:12.00,Signs,,0,0,0,,Akito Kanie
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.33,0:03:14.75,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kanie used to look like this?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.75,0:03:16.92,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's no wonder I didn't recognize him.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.61,0:03:24.74,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Wait, now that I think about it, how was it that he recognized me so quickly?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.05,0:03:31.06,Signs,,0,0,0,,Natori
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.97,0:03:28.98,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I guess I really haven't changed much.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.09,0:03:33.72,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,W-Who could that be?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.06,0:03:41.07,Signs,,0,0,0,,Dreams{This is clearly a yearbook design by 夢ふぉと, so I chose the English subtitle "Dreams" from one of their cover designs with this kanji on it. I really tried reading the spine, but couldn't make out everything, so I've left it untranslated.}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.21,0:03:38.22,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,Hello, is this Natori?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.73,0:03:41.07,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,Yes. Umm...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.53,0:03:43.95,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,It's me, Kanie.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.95,0:03:45.65,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,K-Kanie?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.65,0:03:48.15,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,How did you know my number?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.15,0:03:52.79,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,I got it from Konishi, he's the coordinator\N for the alumni association.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.79,0:03:55.70,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,So, umm... Why are you calling?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.05,0:03:59.12,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,Did you know the athletic festival is next week?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.12,0:04:01.25,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,A-Athletic festival?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.25,0:04:03.88,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,You had best get some exercise.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.49,0:04:06.63,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,I'll train with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.63,0:04:10.15,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,I-I'm fine, I don't need you to.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.15,0:04:15.15,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,"Fine," you say? Do you really think you have that kind of stamina, Miss 25-year-old?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.15,0:04:17.52,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,W-Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.45,0:04:19.78,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,OK, we'll start tomorrow, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.19,0:04:22.06,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,Don't forget your gym uniform.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.06,0:04:24.04,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,H-Hold on!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.21,0:04:28.46,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,{\i1}An athletic festival, huh?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.46,0:04:31.14,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,{\i1}How is that going to work out for me?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.69,0:04:12.89,Songs (Overlap),,0,0,0,,Who could have predicted this reunion?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.89,0:04:20.77,Songs (Overlap),,0,0,0,,I reel in this thread of memory, and use it to spin my tale
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.77,0:04:25.65,Songs (Overlap),,0,0,0,,Why are you all pushy one minute,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.65,0:04:31.41,Songs (Overlap),,0,0,0,,and then gentle the next?
