Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.75,0:04:36.91,Songs,,0,0,0,,As long as the two of us share this secret
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.91,0:04:42.47,Songs,,0,0,0,,it will be the light that guides you
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.47,0:04:47.25,Songs,,0,0,0,,to somewhere in the yet-unknowable future
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.25,0:04:51.69,Songs,,0,0,0,,I'm telling you, it's okay to optimistic
